       <p>I'm a Media Support Specialist from Italy, currently living in London and working for the BBC.</p>
 
        <p>My  career began with Digital Video Editing. I studied Arts, Music, Theatre and Film for 5 years between Turin and Bologna and later on I've achieved a Master in Digital Media in London.</p>
 
        <p>I have fifteen years experience in Video  Production and my focus now is on editing, interactive media and coding.</p>
 
        <p>I'm passionate about building compelling stories  using creativity and a mix of video production, coding and web design.</p>
 
